        <li><a href="https://people.wku.edu/charles.smith/essays/2004HistPhilLifeSciBkRev.pdf" target="_top">&quot;Alfred 
          Russel Wallace on Man: A Famous 'Change of Mind'--Or Not?&quot;</a> 
          (an essay published in late 2004).<br />
